TI  - Design and extensibility analysis of a variable buoyancy system for small autonomous underwater vehicles
T2  - INDUSTRIAL ROBOT-THE INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ROBOTICS RESEARCH AND APPLICATION
LA  - English
KW  - Autonomous underwater vehicles
KW  - Variable buoyancy system (VBS)
