TI  - Robust Prescribed-Time ESO-Based Practical Predefined-Time SMC for Benthic AUV Trajectory-Tracking Control with Uncertainties and Environment Disturbance
T2  - JOURNAL OF MARINE SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING
