TI  - Super-Twisting Sliding Mode Control for the Trajectory Tracking of Underactuated USVs with Disturbances
T2  - JOURNAL OF MARINE SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING
LA  - English
KW  - unmanned surface vehicle
