TI  - Formation Control for UAV-USVs Heterogeneous System with Collision Avoidance Performance
T2  - JOURNAL OF MARINE SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING
LA  - English
KW  - heterogeneous formation control system
KW  - UAV-USVs
KW  - extended state observer
KW  - collision avoidance
